              <p class="text-xs" style="color: var(--muted-foreground)">Conventional alternatives to reverse mortgages.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/estate-mortgage-renewal/" class="rounded-lg p-4" style="border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card)">
              <p class="font-semibold text-sm mb-1" style="color: var(--primary)">Estate Mortgage Renewal</p>
              <p class="text-xs" style="color: var(--muted-foreground)">How reverse mortgages interact with inheritance.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/mortgage-renewal-calculator/" class="rounded-lg p-4" style="border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card)">
              <p class="font-semibold text-sm mb-1" style="color: var(--primary)">Renewal Calculator</p>
              <p class="text-xs" style="color: var(--muted-foreground)">Model conventional payments before committing to reverse.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/mortgage-renewal-term-lengths/" class="rounded-lg p-4" style="border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card)">
              <p class="font-semibold text-sm mb-1" style="color: var(--primary)">Term Lengths</p>
              <p class="text-xs" style="color: var(--muted-foreground)">Shorter terms may ease transition to reverse later.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/renewal-vs-refinancing/" class="rounded-lg p-4" style="border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card)">
              <p class="font-semibold text-sm mb-1" style="color: var(--primary)">Renewal vs. Refinance</p>
              <p class="text-xs" style="color: var(--muted-foreground)">A reverse mortgage is technically a refinance.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/mortgage-broker-renewal/" class="rounded-lg p-4" style="border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card)">
              <p class="font-semibold text-sm mb-1" style="color: var(--primary)">Using a Broker</p>
              <p class="text-xs" style="color: var(--muted-foreground)">Brokers can quote all three reverse mortgage providers.</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <aside class="w-full lg:w-64 flex-shrink-0">
        <div class="sticky top-6 space-y-6">
          <div class="rounded-lg p-5" style="background: var(--accent); border: 1px solid var(--border)">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-3" style="color: var(--primary)">On This Page</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
              <li><a href="#" style="color: var(--secondary)">When It Makes Sense</a></li>
              <li><a href="#" style="color: var(--secondary)">Canadian Providers</a></li>
              <li><a href="#" style="color: var(--secondary)">How Much You Can Borrow</a></li>
              <li><a href="#" style="color: var(--secondary)">Long-Term Trade-Off</a></li>
              <li><a href="#" style="color: var(--secondary)">No Negative Equity</a></li>
              <li><a href="#" style="color: var(--secondary)">Alternatives</a></li>
              <li><a href="#" style="color: var(--secondary)">Switching Process</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg p-5 text-white" style="background: var(--primary)">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-3">Reverse Mortgage Consultation</h3>
            <p class="text-sm mb-4 opacity-90">We quote CHIP, Equitable Flex, and Bloom side-by-side — and compare against conventional renewal alternatives. No cost, no pressure.</p>
            <a href="/book-a-call/" class="block w-full text-center rounded-lg py-2 font-semibold text-sm" style="background: var(--secondary)">
              Book a Free Call
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </article>

  <div class="fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 z-40 border-t p-4 lg:hidden" style="background: var(--background); border-color: var(--border)">
    <a href="/book-a-call/" class="block w-full rounded-lg text-center py-3 font-semibold text-white" style="background: var(--primary)">
      Get a Free Broker Consultation
    </a>
  </div>

  <section class="py-16 text-white" style="background: var(--primary)">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Compare Reverse vs. Conventional Renewal</h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-8 opacity-90">Every senior's situation is different. We'll quote both paths side by side and help you — and your family — make the right decision.</p>
      <a href="/book-a-call/" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-lg px-10 py-4 font-bold text-lg hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity" style="background: var(--secondary)">
        Book Your Free Renewal Strategy Call
